dend

Class Edge

  • java.lang.Object
    • dend.Edge

  • public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the edge between two vertices in an undirected graph. Modified based on Edge.java of the ImageJ AnalyzeSkeleton_ plugin by Ignacio Arganda-Carreras.

    For more information about the original plugin, visit the AnalyzeSkeleton home page: http://fiji.sc/AnalyzeSkeleton

    Author:
    Diana Bank, Elena Zhong, Chun Han Lab, Cornell University

        Parameters:
        v1 - first vertex
        v2 - second vertex
        slabs - list of slab voxels
        length - calibrated edge length
        color3rd - average color value of the inner third
        color - average color value
        length_ra - calibrated edge length calculated with running average ofer 5 Pixel
